high_descs: Move to the sink across the room.
Pick up the fork out of the sink.
Move to the refrigerator and open the door.
Put the fork in the glass inside the fridge.
Pick up the glass with the fork in it.  Close the fridge.
Move across the room to the sink.
Place the fork and glass in the bottom of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Gather glass & fork from refrigerator to place in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink
Pick up the metal fork from the kitchen sink
Turn right and walk around the kitchen to the fridge
Put the fork into the cup inside the fridge
Pick up the cup from the fridge
Turn left and walk back over to the kitchen sink
Put the cup with fork into the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: Put the cup with fork into the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn left, then right, then left to face the sink.
Pick up the fork from in the sink.
Turn right, then right, then left at the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the fork in the cup that is in the fridge.
Pick up the cup from the fridge.
Turn left, then left, then right to go to the sink.
Place the cup in the center of the sink, to the left of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it in the sink.
